---
import { Users } from "lucide-react";
---

<section id="about" class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="container px-4 md:px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-4 text-center">
      <Users className="h-16 w-16 text-blue-500" />
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl">About Space Digital Media</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-[700px] text-gray-500 md:text-xl">
        With over a decade of experience serving Nagercoil and the Kanyakumari District, Space Digital Media is committed to delivering top-notch printing solutions and customized corporate gifts. Our team of local experts ensures that every project meets the highest standards of quality and
        creativity, tailored to the unique needs of businesses in our region.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-primary/10">
  <div class="container px-4 md:px-6">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl text-center mb-8">Serving Nagercoil and Beyond</h2>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-500 md:text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Space Digital Media is proud to be Nagercoil's go-to digital printing solution. We extend our services to businesses and individuals throughout the Kanyakumari District, including areas like Thuckalay, Marthandam, and Kanyakumari. Our local expertise and commitment to quality make us the
      preferred choice for all printing needs in the region.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
